Kylie Jenner has shared a set of photos on Instagram that reveal just how extreme her curves are. 
Sitting on the floor in a nude thong and matching crop top, the 19 year old flaunted her toned stomach and curvaceous bum. 
Kylie smoulders as her long dark hair tumbles down her back. Kylie Jenner showed off her enviable curves (Photo: Instagram) 
The lip kit mogul wears dark eyeshadow that highlights her natural beauty. 
The shots shared with her 84.1m Instagram followers quickly racked up over 2.8m likes. 
Last week, the star used her Instagram page to send her support to her best friend Jordyn Woods after her father passed away from cancer. Kylie Jenner showcased her makeup (Photo: Internet Unknown) 
Taking to social media on Thursday, devastated Jordyn revealed her dad had only been diagnosed with the disease two weeks ago. 
Alongside a picture of her dad, she wrote: "Last night heaven got another angel. My Daddy. Just two short weeks ago he was diagnosed with cancer and by that time it was too late. 
"I appreciate everyone's kind words and it means the world to me. It still doesn't feel real. Forever and Always." Kylie Jenner wore a nude thong and crop top for the photo shoot (Photo: Internet Unknown) 
She also shared a picture of her entire family and simply wrote, "My angel". 
Kylie later shared a picture of them and said she was crying with her. 
"My Fire Ox, My Brother, My Soul Sister. Give Jordy & her family some support and prayers right now. I love you the long way @jordynwoods . The other half of me .. When you cry I cry." Kylie Jenner and Jordyn Woods (Photo: Instagram) 
Hailey Baldwin also sent her support, writing: “This girl right here puts a smile on my face every single time I’m in her presence. 
"An incredible, strong soul. I love you @jordynwoods.” Like us on Facebook
